text: Hiis metis eadem XX manse circumgirantur.
Ðis synd þara twentig hida landgemere æt Wenbeorgan of smitan on þone stan of þam stanæ on þone ealdan an of þan eadenne innan lentan.
Of lentan on gean þone stream on þone greatan þorne stent bæ lentan scaðe of þan þornæ on þa weter furh innan smalan broc.
Of smalan broce on þan stenihte hlinc.
Of þam stenihte hlince on glottos wylle.
Of glottes wylle on wylles heafod on wylles heafodde on Wulfheres cumbe of Wulfheres cumbe on Wulfheres clif of Wulfheres clife on þa furh.
Of þære furh on Winfles beorg of þan beorge on þonne holan stan of þam holan stane on þone haran stan.
Of þam haran stane on þa holan wannan on þone wugan hlinc.
Of þam rugan hlincæ on þone durnen crundel of ðam durnen crundelle on þone þorn of ham þorne on þone stan.
Of ham stanæ on þa dic.
To ðere dic ende on þere dic ende on þone wogan hlinc.
Of ðam wogan hlince on þa catt hola.
Of þan catt holan on Wenbeorge of þan beorge on þone mycelan cumbe.
Of mycelan cumbe on smalan combe of smalan cumbe on þone ealdan treow stede of þam ealdan treow stede on þa wogan apoldran of þere wogan apoldran on folces dic.
Of folces dic on Ealcheres dic of Ealcheres dic.
